{"lemma":"سَنامِ","slug":"سَنامِ","root":"س.ن.م","root_slug":"س-ن-م","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ن-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n20980"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a camel hump","tags":["countable"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sa.naːm/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20980","headword_ar":"سَنَامٌ","root":"snm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"of the camel, (S,) of the he-camel and of the she-camel, [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hump;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"highest part of the back:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in substance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is to the camel like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloyap","text_ar":"اَلْيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fat of the tail"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the sheep:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asonimapN","text_ar":"اَسْنِمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) [and app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asonaAmN","text_ar":"اَسْنَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, as seems to be indicated by an explanation of this latter pl. in what follows]. Hence, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nisaA='N EalaY ruw^uwsihin~a","text_ar":"نِسَا=ءٌ عَلَى رُوُوسِهِنَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaA^asonimapi Albuxoti","text_ar":"كَاَسْنِمَةِ البُخْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Women upon whose heads are the like of the humps of the Bactrian camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning such as wind the head-coverings as turbans upon their heads so as to enlarge them [in appearance] thereby. (TA.) [Hence, also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanaAmu","text_ar":"سَنَامُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAqapi","text_ar":"النَّاقَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The name of a star in the constellation of Cassiopea:"},{"kind":"text","text":"mentioned by Freytag, with a reference to Ideler Untersuch. p. 84.] ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"highest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"highest part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything: (TA:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"best,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"choice part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,) of anything; (TA;) because the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanaAm","text_ar":"سَنَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the best, or the choice part, of what is in the camel. (M.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asonimapu Alr~imaAli","text_ar":"اَسْنِمَةُ الرِّمَالِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The protuberant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated, parts of the sands;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as being likened to the hump of the she-camel: (M, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asonimapu Alr~amoli","text_ar":"اَسْنِمَةُ الرَّمْلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the backs of the sands, that rise from the main portions thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanaAmu AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"سَنَامُ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baHor","text_ar":"بَحْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] (S, TA [in some copies of the S"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHor","text_ar":"نَحْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", perhaps correctly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najod","text_ar":"نَجْد"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated, part"},{"kind":"text","text":"])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the middle of the land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanaAmu Aln~aEoli","text_ar":"سَنَامُ النَّعْلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The rising part of the middle of the upper side of the sandal, which is in the place of the hollow of the foot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 559.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asonaAmu naArK","text_ar":"اَسْنَامُ نَارٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The highest parts of a fire:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(EM p. 156, and TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asonaAm","text_ar":"اَسْنَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"being pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanaAmN","text_ar":"سَنَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"highest part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing. (EM ubi suprà.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanaAmu Almajodi","text_ar":"سَنَامُ المَجْدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The highest"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of a people]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of glory."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","TA","Msb","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}